{"tid":980960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"餵5米鱷魚慘變食物　她墜池遭啃爛半個身體消失","createTime":"2019-01-14T01:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T10:21:00.000Z","uid":32511,"like":147,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"02c70b997cb8adea50c5aa7ed7f01b13f5140755","tid":980960,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T01:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WUGKsu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WUGKsu.png&h=060db035&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQaFZ0R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQaFZ0R.png&h=c4baf378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n死狀太淒慘！印尼北蘇拉威西省米納哈薩縣一名44歲的女子迪西塔（Deasy Tuwo），在餵食公司飼養的鱷魚時失足墜池，結果慘遭一隻5公尺長的鱷魚啃食，屍體被打撈上岸時已經被撕咬破爛、右上半身疑被鱷魚吃掉。<br />\n <br />\n據《Tribun news》報導，迪西塔在當地一間由日本人開設的珍珠養殖公司CV Yosiki工作，1月11日上午，迪西塔的同事因為找不到她，便開始搜索公司各個區域，但始終沒有發現迪西塔的蹤跡，後來在經過鱷魚池時發現有疑似人體的漂浮物，於是急忙報警，結果真的打撈起了迪西塔的屍體。<br />\n <br />\n迪西塔在該公司已經工作15年，除了日常工作外，每天早上、晚上都會去餵鱷魚吃金槍魚、雞肉或豬肉，同事不解迪西塔為何會突然遭遇噩運，詳細發生原因還有待進一步調查。"},{"pid":"8be7454914322316eb3211b1f2a63a57240e98cf","tid":980960,"uid":224561,"like":145,"dislike":8,"score":137,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T01:15:17.000Z","msg":"呢啲就有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b127fe1da5706ea8a482968a187349cb259b12","tid":980960,"uid":21423,"like":142,"dislike":251,"score":-109,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T01:18:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"977009b080df86ff3e0d48993c48a28e45918f2a","tid":980960,"uid":35914,"like":2,"dislike":298,"score":-296,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T01:20:44.000Z","msg":"點解唔比佢死埋，救埋淨低個一半上黎就唔洗死？"},{"pid":"4a334c66b8a7b69f700ae8909acc7355915a4265","tid":980960,"uid":12021,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T01:21:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1eaa97e9ca2a64d9e60d01f